%% Tenant isolation: server-side context, scoped queries, admin override

flowchart TD
  U[User] --> S[Session / cookie]
  S --> TC[Current tenant context]
  TC --> M{Tenant membership OK?}
  M -->|yes| SV[Service layer]
  M -->|no| X[Reject / 403]
  SV --> Q[tenantId-scoped query]
  Q --> DB[(DB: tenant-only data)]

  R1["Rule: tenantId server-derived"]
  R2["Rule: do not trust client tenant id"]
  R3["Rule: records scoped by tenantId"]
  R4["Rule: block cross-tenant in services"]

  R1 -.-> TC
  R2 -.-> TC
  R3 -.-> Q
  R4 -.-> SV

  GA[Global admin] --> OP[Override path with audit]
  OP --> SV
